  "key_insight": "The largest WIP band at May 14, 2026 is 'Open' with 1783 items in flight. The thicker that band is on the chart, the more work is queued or in-progress at that stage; the steeper the line bordering it, the faster items are arriving into the stage.",
  "next_actions": [
